cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with action classification using 3D convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new block for modeling correlations between channels of a 3D CNN, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses transfer learning from 2D CNNs, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
